Detailed Description

This extension header provides a mapping between a GUID and an OEM file type.

Field Documentation

EFI_FIRMWARE_VOLUME_EXT_ENTRY EFI_FIRMWARE_VOLUME_EXT_ENTRY_OEM_TYPE::Hdr

Standard extension entry, with the type EFI_FV_EXT_TYPE_OEM_TYPE.

UINT32 EFI_FIRMWARE_VOLUME_EXT_ENTRY_OEM_TYPE::TypeMask

A bit mask, one bit for each file type between 0xC0 (bit 0) and 0xDF (bit 31). If a bit is '1', then the GUID entry exists in Types. If a bit is '0' then no GUID entry exists in Types.

EFI_GUID EFI_FIRMWARE_VOLUME_EXT_ENTRY_OEM_TYPE::Types[1]

An array of GUIDs, each GUID representing an OEM file type.
